verses.rendering:
My heart overflows with a good word;
I address my work to the king.
My tongue is the pen of a skilled scribe.

You are the most handsome among the sons of humanity;
grace is poured upon your lips.
Therefore God has blessed you forever.

You love righteousness and hate wickedness;
therefore God, your God, has anointed you
with the oil of joy beyond your companions.

In embroidered garments she is led to the king;
virgins, her companions, follow after her —
they are brought to you.
